    "title": "Job Opening Category Manager at Zepto South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Join the Zepto South Asia Partners family as a Category Manager in Pimpri-Chinchwad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Zepto South Asia Partners:\nZepto South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zepto South Asia Partners!",
